title: Assistant Cook
description: Assistant Cook at Babu's, Zurich. Full-time position based at Löwenstrasse 1, 8001 Zurich. Workload 100%, various shifts Monday to Sunday. The cook works in a team of 5 to 6 employees preparing all food served. Responsible for maintaining kitchen hygiene standards, mise en place, cleaning tasks, and dishwashing support. Requirements include at least 2 years kitchen experience, good German and/or English skills, social competence, passion, willingness to learn, and teamwork. Babu's offers a modern workplace, open culture, familiar atmosphere, opportunities for internal promotion, regulated working hours, performance-based salary, and employee discounts.

sections.title: About Us
sections.staticContent:
Babu's is a dynamic company that stands for simplicity, heartiness and enjoyment - right in the vibrant heart of Zurich.
With two coffee houses in District 1, a bakery in District 3 and our production facility in Zurich Binz, we provide our guests with freshly baked delicacies, home-made dishes and high-quality coffee every day. Whether for breakfast, brunch, lunch or a relaxed coffee break - we create enjoyable moments in a cozy atmosphere and invite you to linger.
Are you motivated to become part of our team?

sections.title: YOUR TASKS
sections.staticContent: The cook works in a team of 5 to 6 employees and prepares all the food served at Babu's. He/she is jointly responsible for ensuring that hygiene standards are maintained in the kitchen at all times and is also jointly responsible for the mise en place in the kitchen. As a team member, he/she is also responsible for various cleaning tasks and, if necessary, also stands by the dishwasher.

sections.title: APPLICATION INSTRUCTIONS
sections.staticContent: We look forward to receiving your application with the usual documents by e-mail to info@babus.ch.
